ASSESSMENT_LOWER.name: lower
ASSESSMENT_LOWER.description: Only applies those metrics specified in the vector that result in a lower or equal overall score

ASSESSMENT_HIGHER.name: higher
ASSESSMENT_HIGHER.description: Only applies those metrics specified in the vector that result in a higher or equal overall score

ASSESSMENT_LOWER_METRIC.name: lower metric
ASSESSMENT_LOWER_METRIC.description: Only applies those metrics specified in the vector that are ranked lower or equal to the other metric

ASSESSMENT_HIGHER_METRIC.name: higher metric
ASSESSMENT_HIGHER_METRIC.description: Only applies those metrics specified in the vector that are ranked higher or equal to the other metric

ASSESSMENT_ALL.name: all
ASSESSMENT_ALL.description: Applies all parts of the vector
